{"tid":380613,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"(片)Yanny原來都係港女臭格，法官大人😾","createTime":"2017-08-30T08:56:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-02T04:44:27.000Z","uid":49648,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"16e371667a3a98a384262dd5cee5549a8fb84489","tid":380613,"uid":49648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T08:56:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170830/bkn-20170830000030815-0830_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170830%2Fbkn-20170830000030815-0830_00862_001.html&d=FpXqscEZCIuu4ZQJylopv54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=65e06515\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170830/bkn-20170830000030815-0830_00862_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\nSuper Girls成員之一的Yanny（陳穎欣），月前被踢爆因為爭「有米」監製Gareth（陳考威），與另一成員Heidi（李靜儀）鬧不和，最終Yanny還撼贏了Heidi，與Gareth發展戀情。<br />\n<br />\n揼骨「梳乎」<br />\n<br />\n而大前日（27日）Yanny趁颱風「帕卡」風勢逐漸減弱，於傍晚時分以勝利者姿態與Gareth拍拖出巡到佐敦，富貴Gareth更以價值約八十萬港元的黑色Audi接載伊人，Yanny下車後到了附近按摩店，男友泊車後即入店內會合Yanny，兩人揼骨「梳乎」一番後，於晚上八時許才離開。<br />\n<br />\n全程面黑黑<br />\n<br />\nYanny與男友及後途經二手錶舖時，她便拉着男友於櫥窗前睇錶，看似想買錶的Yanny手指指揀選心頭好，見她還施冧功不時肉緊地攬住男友咬耳仔，不過男友反應冷淡，不為所動的Gareth更拖着Yanny匆匆離開，並到附近食店平食米線，兩人坐下後各自點了食物，但買錶不成的Yanny全程面黑黑，還嘴扁扁睥住男友，面對面坐的二人完全零交流各自撳電話，冷戰期間Yanny竟突然起身走人，Gareth見狀雖表現愕然，但未有上前追截女友。<br />\n<br />\n電話攻勢狂冧<br />\n<br />\n嬲到撇下男友的Yanny及後步往對面街的麵店獨自食雲吞麵，期間Gareth似以電話攻勢狂氹女友，見Yanny開餐時不停低頭撳電話，又多次甜甜笑，看來已原諒男友，埋單後她便死死地氣往會合男友，Gareth亦十分識做，一手拿着外賣一手拖着女友於她耳邊喃喃細語，兩人大耍花槍後便往取車離開。"},{"pid":"d05119ac0da80337f65d784a4b9ba83f00fa9006","tid":380613,"uid":49648,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T09:11:15.000Z","msg":"Heidi 好好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82581be0e9a54c0477debd4e60345a7f5c535542","tid":380613,"uid":20302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T09:14:27.000Z","msg":"食完應該好快俾人飛"},{"pid":"d52d526003a5917b0e35b72cccaf8aba759ac5f4","tid":380613,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T16:58:22.000Z","msg":"臭雞"},{"pid":"938b513d71ec7aabe05922eef8271af115f27bf2","tid":380613,"uid":81995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T00:20:59.000Z","msg":"留名等睇中出即飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"523abc2ccc9d97ed9cde91c0e557537da3a2850f","tid":380613,"uid":3647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T00:59:06.000Z","msg":"Yanny 比佢 heidi 留番比我"},{"pid":"54440bf2ff6e353fda7b0044b091e60d63128221","tid":380613,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T04:22:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20151018/photo/bkn-20151018070047859-1018_00862_001_12p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20151018%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20151018070047859-1018_00862_001_12p.jpg&h=ae55c2f8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"413b5b881aca31ba65c137cd2da5549e52bb6a80","tid":380613,"uid":71393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T04:44:27.000Z","msg":"heidi 冇波嫁嘛"}]}